metadata.name: The Meta Robbers #1
metadata.description: 4269 Meta Robbers breaking out of the Vaults!!! The Meta Robbers came to the blockchain to rehabilitate people, places, and things, through community activation and educational development. Use your meta robber to learn, build, and grow!!! more will be revealed soon. (The Meta Robbers are the foundational product from 'The Meta Bucks.' It is intended as a not for profit digital collectible aimed to safe harbor community assets and help the meta bucks holders access small grant funding for random acts of kindness towards people, places, and things! legal filing for non profit status coming soon.)
